  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Jump</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3448860/extras/4dd5f6fab7a575b944c8a36193cceb7f.poster.avif?t=1747138443\" width=800 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3448860/extras/4dd5f6fab7a575b944c8a36193cceb7f.webm?t=1747138443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3448860/extras/4dd5f6fab7a575b944c8a36193cceb7f.mp4?t=1747138443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>and Roll</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3448860/extras/7147f709aa7578e7365a37bc6ee87a68.poster.avif?t=1747138443\" width=800 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3448860/extras/7147f709aa7578e7365a37bc6ee87a68.webm?t=1747138443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3448860/extras/7147f709aa7578e7365a37bc6ee87a68.mp4?t=1747138443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Simple Game, A Tough Challenge</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mountain 78</strong> is a game about climbing a mountain using only three jumps at a time. Every move counts—one mistake and you could fall all the way down.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s inspired by the \"foddian\" genre and precision-based games where losing progress is part of the challenge.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Why \"78\"?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s there to help you remember a Japanese proverb:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Fall seven times, stand up eight.\"</i> (七転び八起き, <i>Nanakorobi yaoki</i>)</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A climbing challenge where every jump matters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Without narrative dialogues</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fireworks for those who reach the top</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Falling and trying again is part of the experience</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Will you reach the top?</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Jump</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3448860/extras/4dd5f6fab7a575b944c8a36193cceb7f.poster.avif?t=1747138443\" width=800 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3448860/extras/4dd5f6fab7a575b944c8a36193cceb7f.webm?t=1747138443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3448860/extras/4dd5f6fab7a575b944c8a36193cceb7f.mp4?t=1747138443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>and Roll</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3448860/extras/7147f709aa7578e7365a37bc6ee87a68.poster.avif?t=1747138443\" width=800 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3448860/extras/7147f709aa7578e7365a37bc6ee87a68.webm?t=1747138443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3448860/extras/7147f709aa7578e7365a37bc6ee87a68.mp4?t=1747138443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Simple Game, A Tough Challenge</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mountain 78</strong> is a game about climbing a mountain using only three jumps at a time. Every move counts—one mistake and you could fall all the way down.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s inspired by the \"foddian\" genre and precision-based games where losing progress is part of the challenge.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Why \"78\"?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s there to help you remember a Japanese proverb:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Fall seven times, stand up eight.\"</i> (七転び八起き, <i>Nanakorobi yaoki</i>)</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A climbing challenge where every jump matters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Without narrative dialogues</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fireworks for those who reach the top</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Falling and trying again is part of the experience</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Will you reach the top?</strong></p>",
